fields.title: Unpacking Malware using r2
fields.description:
The idea of the training was to go through different malware samples and explain several approaches one could take to unpack them, focusing on different strategies instead of focusing only on the specific steps.

The training was completely hands-on therefore the workflow was to let the attendees attempt each sample and slowly but surely (each N minutes) advance one slide at a time showing them one more clue about how to unpack the sample.
